-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/unilever-nigeria-invested-19-3-billion-last-year-thisday-says.html
(Corrects to say million in headline.)  Unilever Nigeria Plc invested 3
billion naira ($19.3 million) in 2010 to expand its capacity,
ThisDay newspaper reported, citing Chairman Hayford Alile.  To contact the reporter on this story:
